ed automatically. E.g. \"google.com\" also matches \"docs.google.com\".": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "子域名会自动包含。例如\"google.com\"也匹配\"docs.google.com\"。"}}}}, "System Default": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "系统默认"}}}}, "System Prompt": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "系统提示词"}}}}, "Target": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "目标"}}}}, "Target language": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "目标语言"}}}}, "Task": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "任务"}}}}, "Term": {"comment": "Name of the type of dictionary entry that is a technical term.", "isCommentAutoGenerated": true, "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "术语"}}}}, "Term Packs": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "术语包"}}}}, "Terms": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "术语"}}}}, "Terms are sent to the transcription service for better recognition": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "术语会发送到转录服务以提高识别度"}}}}, "Terms help speech recognition identify technical words correctly. Corrections fix common transcription mistakes automatically.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "术语帮助语音识别正确识别技术词汇。纠正自动修复常见转录错误。"}}}}, "Test Microphone": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "测试麦克风"}}}}, "Text inserted": {"comment": "Text shown in a toast notification when text is successfully inserted into a text field.", "extractionState": "stale", "isCommentAutoGenerated": true, "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "文本已插入"}}}}, "Text replaced": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "文本已替换"}}}}, "The file contains no dictionary entries.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "文件不包含词典条目。"}}}}, "The file is not a valid dictionary JSON file.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "文件不是有效的词典 JSON 文件。"}}}}, "The language being spoken. Setting this explicitly improves accuracy.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "正在说的语言。明确设置可提高准确性。"}}}}, "The language change will take effect after restarting DavyWhisper.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "语言更改将在重启 DavyWhisper 后生效。"}}}}, "The notch indicator extends the MacBook notch area to show recording status.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "刘海指示器扩展 MacBook 刘海区域以显示录音状态。"}}}}, "The overlay indicator appears as a floating pill on the screen.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "悬浮指示器显示为屏幕上的浮动胶囊。"}}}}, "This hotkey is also assigned to the %@ slot.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "此快捷键也分配给了 %@ 槽位。"}}}}, "This Week": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "本周"}}}}, "This will permanently delete all stored memories from all plugins. This cannot be undone.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "这将永久删除所有插件中的所有存储记忆。此操作无法撤销。"}}}}, "Time": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "时间"}}}}, "Time Saved": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "节省时间"}}}}, "Timer": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "计时器"}}}}, "To use AI prompts, install an LLM provider (e.g. Groq, OpenAI) from the Integrations tab after setup.": {"extractionState": "stale", "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "tr