tory"}}, "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "清除历史"}}}}, "watchFolder.language": {"localizations": {"en": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "Language"}}, "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "语言"}}}}, "watchFolder.language.auto": {"localizations": {"en": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "Auto-detect"}}, "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "自动检测"}}}}, "watchFolder.description": {"localizations": {"en": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "Watches the selected folder for new audio files and automatically transcribes them."}}, "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "监视所选文件夹中的新音频文件并自动转录。"}}}}, "All engines installed.": {"comment": "A message displayed when all transcription engines installed.", "isCommentAutoGenerated": true, "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "所有引擎已安装。"}}}}, "Default LLM": {"comment": "A label for the default large language model picker in the setup wizard.", "isCommentAutoGenerated": true, "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "默认 LLM"}}}}, "Detect spoken instructions in your dictation (e.g., 'write this as an email') and apply them automatically via LLM.": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "检测您听写中的口头指令（例如“写成一封邮件”）并通过 LLM 自动应用。"}}}}, "Inline Commands": {"localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "内联命令"}}}}, "Install a transcription engine to get started. Each engine needs to download a model before it can be used.": {"comment": "A description under the \"Install a transcription engine\" heading in the Setup Wizard.", "isCommentAutoGenerated": true, "localizations": {"zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "安装转录引擎以开始使用。每个引擎需要下载模型才能使用。"}}}}, "Loading plugins...": {"comment": "A message indicating that the app is loading available transcription plugins.